      "content": "okay i get that but i really need something that works fast cuz i can't sleep at all with this congestion. i read online that some people say a little bit of pseudoephedrine is actually fine since i'm already in my second trimester and past the first one. if i just take one pill, is it really going to do that much damage or am i overthinking it? it feels like a small thing compared to how much this is affecting my daily life.",
